  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to hicolor-icon-theme</title>

    <para>
      The <application>hicolor-icon-theme</application> package
      contains a default fallback theme for implementations of the icon
      theme specification.
    </para>

    &lfs122_checked;

